				\begin{document}$$\hbox {TiO}_2$$\end{document} as well62,63. However, for the codoping (viz. N-Mn, N-Rh, S-Mn and S-Rh) in bulk SrTiO3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
