				\begin{document}$$\hbox {SrTiO}_3$$\end{document} for enhancing the photocatalytic efficiency. We have shown in Ref.64,65 that the substitutional doping is more favorable than the interstitial in TiO2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
