				\begin{document}$$\hbox {SrTiO}_3$$\end{document}. Therefore, we have chosen only the substitutional positions (i.e. metal at Ti or Sr site and nonmetal at O site) for codoping. First, we have determined the thermodynamic stability of codoped TiO2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
